> Download Nodejs
> Install NPM and Node
> List of recommended code editor

https://nodejs.org/en
download - recommend for most users (stable)

// NPM : Node package manager

> it's manage external package or library.
> It automatically install with node

node -v  v22.9.0
npm -v  10.9.0
